{"tid":937981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"17歲啦啦隊長懷孕　男友不想當爸崩潰殺她","createTime":"2018-12-12T02:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T00:35:28.000Z","uid":130626,"like":17,"dislike":523,"uniUserReply":105,"replies":[{"pid":"f1199170eba4310a0ac763992ac22f84a92b8aff","tid":937981,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T02:36:33.000Z","msg":"美國印第安納州一名17歲少女，因為被男友搞大肚子後，沒有馬上告知對方懷孕，等男友得知時，她已懷胎六個月，不能墮胎。男友不想這麼年輕就當爸爸，加上不滿她隱瞞，決定深夜把她約出來滅口，再棄屍到一間餐廳的垃圾桶內。 16歲的美式足球隊員崔喬（Aaron Trejo）與17歲的啦啦隊隊長魯塞朗（Breana Rouhselang）同樣就讀米沙沃卡高中（Mishawaka High School），兩人也住得很近。魯塞朗上周六（8日）晚上11時跟家人說：「要去見孩子的父親」，但一去不返。她的母親周日凌晨1時起床時，見到女兒還沒回家，越想越不對勁，於是到崔喬家詢問女兒的下落，但對方堅稱，魯塞朗從未出現。魯塞朗的母親，因為擔心女兒安危，在凌晨4時半報警。警方展開搜索行動後，周日上午在一間餐廳的垃圾桶內，發現魯塞朗的屍體。警方後來逮捕崔喬，指控他謀殺和殺害胎兒。崔喬坦承殺人，又說兩人見面時吵了一架。他不滿魯塞朗拖了太久才告訴他懷孕的消息，等他知道時已經過了可以墮胎的機會，「我於是採取行動&hellip;我取了她的性命」。崔喬表示，他當晚從家中帶了一把利刀，在兩人見面時用刀刺入魯塞朗的心臟，認為用刀可以迅速將她殺死，讓她死得痛快。而後，他用黑色塑膠袋包住屍體棄屍，又把她的手機及兇刀拋入河中。警方指：「崔喬說他已策劃一周，打算殺死魯塞朗及寶寶，但沒有告訴任何人。」魯塞朗的驗屍報告顯示，她身上有多處刀傷，而她的頸巾綁得非常緊，死前曾經窒息。謀殺案震驚學校，兩人的同學周一早上11時離開教室，為魯塞朗默哀。崔喬會於周二出庭受審。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dT8fR1F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdT8fR1F.png&h=b57cb41c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/huN4LmG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhuN4LmG.png&h=7b6ff417&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vtBtsz1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvtBtsz1.png&h=e3f47e0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qfQ2w1H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqfQ2w1H.png&h=f12a9ce0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2fLub1H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2fLub1H.png&h=60b1e418&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aVDogto.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaVDogto.png&h=f768eb83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80b38f2ad091d9ec67f5dc1258f65990224e7384","tid":937981,"uid":42283,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T02:36:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a360c91f66eabfdfbede86bd35ad6c81fd2c393","tid":937981,"uid":165450,"like":828,"dislike":1,"score":827,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T02:37:51.000Z","msg":"唔想做爸爸就入去做監躉啦.... <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c84887863d6c2eb0f92a6e0bc7536ebb9f0ea386","tid":937981,"uid":43713,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T02:38:38.000Z","msg":"浪費左<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#xm"},{"pid":"2fcbb7f64a52a3d7967f78083da173010ad9544e","tid":937981,"uid":1654,"like":47,"dislike":405,"score":-358,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T02:38:56.000Z","msg":"條女17 歲個樣好老，成個30 歲女人咁，<br />\n條仔 16 歲，就真係成個on9 咁樣"},{"pid":"610a32f0132dcb5cfab91441b4ae6fc028eb90cb","tid":937981,"uid":98223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T02:39:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da0510754d327fd5104511ede5666acf99368d67","tid":937981,"uid":116905,"like":177,"dislike":4,"score":173,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T02:40:01.000Z","msg":"常威你條仆街我要殺咗你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3732af2c1fc25636436db232e846e14f769d074","tid":937981,"uid":66943,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12