母親，因為擔心女兒安危，在凌晨4時半報警。警方展開搜索行動後，周日上午在一間餐廳的垃圾桶內，發現魯塞朗的屍體。警方後來逮捕崔喬，指控他謀殺和殺害胎兒。崔喬坦承殺人，又說兩人見面時吵了一架。他不滿魯塞朗拖了太久才告訴他懷孕的消息，等他知道時已經過了可以墮胎的機會，「我於是採取行動&hellip;我取了她的性命」。崔喬表示，他當晚從家中帶了一把利刀，在兩人見面時用刀刺入魯塞朗的心臟，認為用刀可以迅速將她殺死，讓她死得痛快。而後，他用黑色塑膠袋包住屍體棄屍，又把她的手機及兇刀拋入河中。警方指：「崔喬說他已策劃一周，打算殺死魯塞朗及寶寶，但沒有告訴任何人。」魯塞朗的驗屍報告顯示，她身上有多處刀傷，而她的頸巾綁得非常緊，死前曾經窒息。謀殺案震驚學校，兩人的同學周一早上11時離開教室，為魯塞朗默哀。崔喬會於周二出庭受審。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dT8fR1F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdT8fR1F.png&h=b57cb41c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/huN4LmG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhuN4LmG.png&h=7b6ff417&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vtBtsz1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvtBtsz1.png&h=e3f47e0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qfQ2w1H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqfQ2w1H.png&h=f12a9ce0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2fLub1H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2fLub1H.png&h=60b1e418&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aVDogto.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaVDogto.png&h=f768eb83&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T04:26:29.000Z","msg":"使唔使殺人呀"},{"pid":"51591f9d5799da2edeed866c274448638796711c","tid":937981,"uid":39316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T04:26:58.000Z","msg":"罪犯郁樣睇"},{"pid":"d748fe6222d8efbea9c4e16ecf71b8eeed0708bf","tid":937981,"uid":155197,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T04:27:15.000Z","msg":"義不容情 美國阿康"},{"pid":"5eddcc75930df03901382fe0bacaf63a3e866886","tid":937981,"uid":57633,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"160717210f9d86b5a2f2cb946bebb3272b9420f8","tid":937981,"uid":3117,"like":183,"dislike":3,"score":180,"quote":{"pid":"0f